original: Hallerby, Gunnar Olof, civilingenjör, Göteborg, f. 23/4/11 i Nyköp. G. 39 m. Annalisa Öhlin. Barn: Birgitta f. 41, Mats 46. — Ex. v. Örebro tekn. gymn. 3’3, v. KTH 3i7.. Anist. v. telegr:v. 37-43^ v. SJ sed. 43, teilegr :in!g. v. SJ i Gbg sed. 45.
translated: Hallerby, Gunnar Olof, engineer, Gothenburg, b. 23/4/11 in Nyköp. Married in 1939 to Annalisa Öhlin. Children: Birgitta b. 1941, Mats b. 1946. — Graduated from Örebro Technical High School in 1933, and KTH in 1937. Worked for the telegraph company from 1937-1943, then for SJ from 1943, working in telegraphy until 1945 in Gothenburg.
